clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: Indicated as an adjunct therapy in the treatment of adult HIV 1 infections resistant to therapy with other NNRTIs and antiretroviral agents

contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Clinical trials have shown no prolongation of QT intervals on electrocardiograms after 8 days of dosing
